---
const today = new Date();
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<footer>
	<p>매일 아침, Hacker News의 AI 소식을 모아 Claude가 자동으로 정리합니다. 🤖</p>
	<div class="social-links">
		<a href="https://github.com/imjee1/ai-tool-blog" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
		<a href={`${base}rss.xml`}>RSS</a>
	</div>
	<p class="copyright">&copy; {today.getFullYear()} 오늘의 AI 툴</p>
</footer>
<style>
	footer {
		padding: 2.5em 1em 5em 1em;
		background: linear-gradient(rgba(233, 233, 240, 50%), #fff) no-repeat;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		text-align: center;
		font-size: 0.95em;
	}
	.social-links {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: center;
		gap: 1.2em;
		margin: 0.8em 0;
	}
	.social-links a {
		text-decoration: none;
		color: rgb(var(--gray));
		font-weight: 500;
	}
	.social-links a:hover {
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	.copyright {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.85em;
	}
</style>
